						<div class="postbody">Reminds me of another (rather unimportant) detail: Are positive samples producing positive or negative voltages?<br />The answer to that question isn't that simple because the SNES post amplifier is applying phase inversion to the audio signals.<br />So, if I am not mistaken, a positive voltage on cartridge slot would produce a negative voltage on final SNES audio output.</div>

